3ef\u8bc6\u522b\u7684\u8ba2\u9605\u94fe\u63a5\u3002</p> <ul> <li>\u9879\u76ee\u5730\u5740: youshandefeiyang/sub-web-modify</li> <li>\u4e3b\u8981\u7279\u6027:<ul> <li>\u9884\u7f6e\u4e86\u5927\u91cf\u8fdc\u7a0b\u914d\u7f6e\uff08ACL4SSR \u7b49\uff09</li> <li>\u754c\u9762\u4f18\u5316\uff0c\u652f\u6301\u66f4\u591a\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u9009\u9879</li> </ul> </li> <li>\u90e8\u7f72\u65b9\u5f0f: \u901a\u5e38\u901a\u8fc7 Docker \u90e8\u7f72\u6216\u4f5c\u4e3a\u9759\u6001\u7f51\u9875\u6258\u7ba1\u3002</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/network/proxy/#_3","title":"\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u5de5\u5177","text":""},{"location":"tools/network/proxy/#_4","title":"\u684c\u9762\u7aef","text":"<ul> <li>Clash Verge (Rev)</li> </ul> <pre><code>brew install --cask clash-verge-rev\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/network/proxy/#_5","title":"\u5b89\u5353\u7aef:","text":"<ul> <li>Clash Meta for Android</li> <li>FlClash </li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/note-apps/","title":"\u7b14\u8bb0\u8f6f\u4ef6","text":""},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/","title":"Obsidian","text":""},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/plugins/","title":"Obsidian \u63d2\u4ef6","text":"<ul> <li>obsidian-git</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/themes/","title":"Obsidian \u4e3b\u9898\u6574\u7406","text":"<p>\u8bb0\u5f55\u6211\u5728 Obsidian \u4e2d\u4f7f\u7528/\u5173\u6ce8\u7684\u4e3b\u9898\uff08Themes\uff09\u3002</p>"},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/themes/#_1","title":"\u5f53\u524d\u4f7f\u7528\u4e3b\u9898","text":"<ul> <li>\u540d\u79f0\uff1a</li> <li>\u914d\u8272/\u5b57\u4f53\uff1a</li> <li>\u4e2a\u4eba\u611f\u53d7\uff1a</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/themes/#_2","title":"\u66fe\u4f7f\u7528\u8fc7\u7684\u4e3b\u9898","text":"<ul> <li>\u4e3b\u9898\u540d\uff1a</li> <li>\u4f7f\u7528\u65f6\u95f4\uff1a</li> <li>\u4f18\u70b9\uff1a</li> <li>\u7f3a\u70b9\uff1a</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/themes/#_3","title":"\u60f3\u8bd5\u8bd5\u7684\u4e3b\u9898","text":""},{"location":"tools/note-apps/obsidian/themes/#css-snippets","title":"\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u6837\u5f0f\uff08CSS Snippets\uff09","text":""},{"location":"tools/productivity/","title":"\u6548\u7387\u5de5\u5177","text":""},{"location":"tools/productivity/raycast/","title":"Raycast","text":"<p>macOS \u4e0a\u7684\u6548\u7387\u542f\u52a8\u5668\uff0c\u66ff\u4ee3 Spotlight\u3002</p> <ul> <li>\u5b98\u7f51</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/productivity/raycast/#_1","title":"\u5b89\u88c5\u65b9\u5f0f","text":"<pre><code>brew install --cask raycast\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/","title":"\u7f16\u7a0b\u5de5\u5177","text":""},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/","title":"AI \u7f16\u7a0b\u5de5\u5177\u6574\u7406","text":""},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#antigravity","title":"Antigravity","text":"<p>Google \u63a8\u51fa\u7684 AI IDE\uff0c\u57fa\u4e8e Gemini 3\u3002</p> <ul> <li>\u5b98\u7f51</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#_1","title":"\u5b89\u88c5","text":"<pre><code>brew install --cask antigravity\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#opencode","title":"OpenCode","text":"<ul> <li>\u5b98\u7f51</li> <li>GitHub</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#_2","title":"\u5b89\u88c5","text":"<pre><code>curl -fsSL https://opencode.ai/install | bash\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#oh-my-opencode","title":"Oh My OpenCode","text":"<p>\u57fa\u4e8e OpenCode \u7684\u201c\u7f16\u6392\u5c42\u201d\u63d2\u4ef6\uff1a\u591a Agent \u8c03\u5ea6\u3001Hooks\u3001MCP\u3001LSP \u7b49\u3002</p> <ul> <li>\u5b98\u7f51</li> <li>\u5b89\u88c5\u8bf4\u660e</li> <li>GitHub</li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#_3","title":"\u5b89\u88c5\u65b9\u5f0f","text":"<pre><code>bunx oh-my-opencode install\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#opencode-antigravity-auth","title":"opencode-antigravity-auth","text":"<p>\u4f5c\u7528\uff1a\u8ba9 OpenCode \u901a\u8fc7 OAuth \u4f7f\u7528 Google Antigravity \u7684\u989d\u5ea6\uff0c\u767d\u5ad6 Gemini 3 / Claude \u7b49\u6a21\u578b\u3002</p> <ul> <li>GitHub </li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#oauth","title":"\u6267\u884c OAuth \u767b\u5f55","text":"<pre><code>opencode auth login\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#antigravity-manager","title":"Antigravity-Manager","text":"<p>\u4f5c\u7528\uff1a\u4e13\u4e1a\u7684 Antigravity \u8d26\u53f7\u7ba1\u7406\u4e0e\u4e00\u952e\u5207\u6362 + \u534f\u8bae\u4e2d\u8f6c\uff08OpenAI / Anthropic / Gemini\uff09\uff0c\u505a\u672c\u5730 AI \u7f51\u5173\u3002</p> <ul> <li>GitHub\uff1a  </li> </ul>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#_4","title":"\u5b89\u88c5","text":"<pre><code># 1. \u6dfb\u52a0 Tap\nbrew tap lbjlaq/antigravity-manager https://github.com/lbjlaq/Antigravity-Manager\n\n# 2. \u5b89\u88c5\u5e94\u7528\nbrew install --cask antigravity-tools\n# \u5982\u9047\u5b89\u5168\u9650\u5236\u53ef\u7528\uff1a\n# brew install --cask --no-quarantine antigravity-tools\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"tools/programming/ai/#quotio","title":"quotio","text":"<ul> <li>Github</li> </ul>"}]}